Fix syntax bug that didn't match all comments.
Fix syntax table bug that didn't match //$blah.
Compile files using the --update option.

Support a custom output directory for compiled files.

Merge pull request #8 from samh/master

Fixed quotes in single-line (//) comments.

Fixed quotes in single-line (//) comments.

Single-line ('//'-style) comments are now parsed as part of the syntax table
instead of using font-lock. References:

http://www.emacswiki.org/emacs/EmacsSyntaxTable
http://www.gnu.org/software/emacs/manual/html_node/elisp/Syntax-Flags.html
org-mode doc fix
README tip hide compilation buffer
Version number added, and customizable scss-sass-options added. Thanks @haxney
New regex that matches errors 'on line x of file in section \n from line x of file...', for example undefined mixin errors.
New regex for variables
Fix for compilation of SCSS-files that are placed in folders with names containing "scss"
Small fix for files with spaces in their path.
Add (require 'flymake) because we use the flymake-allowed-file-name-masks variable.
Changed URL to git repository
Added README
Added flymake support
Documentation string  fix
Changed use of (buffer-name) to var buffer-file-name which makes more sense and works with `uniquify' mode.
Fixed SCSS comments to adhere http://www.emacswiki.org/cgi-bin/wiki/ElispAreaConventions
Added inline comment support to sccs-mode.el.
Scss cleanup
